00:11:03.502 --> 00:11:05.927
But my experience with meditation allowed me

272
00:11:05.927 --> 00:11:07.775
to become completely passive,

273
00:11:07.775 --> 00:11:09.175
and to sit quietly within,

274
00:11:09.775 --> 00:11:11.350
and look out through this man's eyes,

