00:11:11.350 --> 00:11:13.280
at a world I had never seen before.

276
00:11:13.770 --> 00:11:15.191
I discovered almost immediately,

277
00:11:15.191 --> 00:11:17.927
that I could access his thoughts, his emotions,

278
00:11:17.927 --> 00:11:20.361
his feelings, his memories, his judgments.

279
00:11:20.687 --> 00:11:22.596
I began to track his thought train,

280
00:11:22.596 --> 00:11:24.504
as though I cou-- or my own.

281
00:11:25.244 --> 00:11:27.972
Now, he was unaware of the fact that I was there.

282
00:11:29.242 --> 00:11:30.419
At that time.

283
00:11:30.419 --> 00:11:31.161
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

284
00:11:31.161 --> 00:11:31.745
<v ->In the beginning.</v>

285
00:11:31.745 --> 00:11:33.144
He was unaware of me.

286
00:11:33.567 --> 00:11:37.089
This man is a man of Hawaiian ancestry.

287
00:11:37.492 --> 00:11:39.262
But he's not living in Hawaii.

288
00:11:39.262 --> 00:11:42.278
He's living somewhere on the coast of Western North America,

289
00:11:42.748 --> 00:11:45.424
in a slice of time which is different from this one.

290
00:11:46.478 --> 00:11:48.859
If I've got this right, and I believe I do,

291
00:11:49.238 --> 00:11:53.409
this man lives in a time 247 generations

292
00:11:53.979 --> 00:11:56.270
after the collapse of Western civilization.

293
00:11:56.740 --> 00:11:58.012
After the collapse of the world

294
00:11:58.012 --> 00:11:59.654
that we all take so much for granted.

295
00:11:59.884 --> 00:12:01.255
Now, if you multiply this out,

296
00:12:01.255 --> 00:12:04.569
this comes out to, roughly, 5,000 years.

297
00:12:05.729 --> 00:12:06.944
If I've got this right,

298
00:12:07.694 --> 00:12:09.587
I was having a look at the future,

299
00:12:09.587 --> 00:12:12.149
5,000 years into the future,

300
00:12:12.517 --> 00:12:15.194
through the eyes and soul of a man,

301
00:12:16.485 --> 00:12:20.320
who seemed very familiar to me, in the beginning.

302
00:12:20.950 --> 00:12:24.209
Now, in this first episode, I was merged with this man,

303
00:12:24.209 --> 00:12:25.779
for 18 hours of his time,

304
00:12:26.129 --> 00:12:28.121
as he was leaving his community,

305
00:12:28.741 --> 00:12:32.586
and engaging on a voyage of geographic investigation,

306
00:12:32.586 --> 00:12:36.004
into the interior of the lost continent of America.

307
00:12:36.378 --> 00:12:38.970
Now, when I talk about this with big conferences,

308
00:12:38.970 --> 00:12:41.202
there's still a side of Hank Wesselman, the scientist,

309
00:12:41.202 --> 00:12:42.498
that steps back and says,

310
00:12:42.498 --> 00:12:44.826
"Hank, did you really say that to these people?

311
00:12:44.826 --> 00:12:48.042
"Time traveling, involved with spirit possession.

312
00:12:48.042 --> 00:12:49.986
"Possessing another man's body,

313
00:12:49.986 --> 00:12:52.640
"looking out through his eyes and soul at another world?"

314
00:12:52.640 --> 00:12:54.474
<v Regina>I'll bet the quantum physicists are saying,</v>

