00:12:57.756 --> 00:13:01.752
"that time is not linear, and to be able to experience

317
00:13:01.752 --> 00:13:04.506
"an existence in the past or the future or the present

318
00:13:04.506 --> 00:13:06.100
"is all one," right?

319
00:13:06.186 --> 00:13:08.346
<v ->Well I didn't know very much about the quantum world then.</v>

