00:13:08.850 --> 00:13:10.500
<v ->I didn't know about the zero point field, for example.</v>

322
00:13:10.500 --> 00:13:11.254
<v Regina>Yes, exactly.</v>

323
00:13:11.254 --> 00:13:13.776
<v ->And that's the field I was accessing, to find this man.</v>

324
00:13:13.776 --> 00:13:14.524
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

325
00:13:14.634 --> 00:13:16.811
<v ->Now, Spiritwalker is the story</v>

