00:13:16.811 --> 00:13:20.404
of how I had 12 of these episodes over a four year period,

327
00:13:20.404 --> 00:13:22.238
while living on my farm in Hawaii.

328
00:13:22.876 --> 00:13:26.230
So, in a sense, the whole story takes place in Hawaii.

329
00:13:26.230 --> 00:13:28.660
But it also takes place in the future,

330
00:13:29.000 --> 00:13:32.763
as this man engages this-- in this extraordinary journey,

331
00:13:32.763 --> 00:13:35.483
across the wilderness of North America,

332
00:13:36.253 --> 00:13:40.257
and finds the descendants of our once great civilization.

333
00:13:40.257 --> 00:13:41.207
He finds them.

334
00:13:41.207 --> 00:13:42.740
Now, I wouldn't dream of spoiling this

335
00:13:42.740 --> 00:13:45.252
interesting story for your readers because this is all

336
00:13:45.252 --> 00:13:48.244
very carefully laid-out in this book Spiritwalker,

337
00:13:48.244 --> 00:13:50.760
in which I try to weave together

338
00:13:50.760 --> 00:13:53.250
these numinous epiphanies,

339
00:13:53.250 --> 00:13:55.172
with my ordinary life,

340
00:13:55.172 --> 00:13:57.764
looking for patterns of reason and causality.

341
00:13:57.764 --> 00:13:58.504
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

342
00:13:58.504 --> 00:14:00.331
See, the scientist is always trying to figure it out.

343
00:14:00.331 --> 00:14:01.243
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

344
00:14:01.483 --> 00:14:04.709
<v ->And so, that book is really my personal journal,</v>

345
00:14:04.709 --> 00:14:06.501
of my Shamanic initiation crisis.

346
00:14:06.501 --> 00:14:08.257
<v Regina>It's a fabulous book, mmhmm.</v>

347
00:14:08.257 --> 00:14:10.787
<v ->The second book in the trilogy, Medicinemaker,</v>

