00:14:10.787 --> 00:14:12.775
is about how I became a Medicine Man.

349
00:14:12.775 --> 00:14:14.223
It's really about my recovery.

350
00:14:14.733 --> 00:14:17.713
And the third book, Visionseeker, is about training.

351
00:14:17.713 --> 00:14:20.237
It's about my training in the Shamanic tradition,

352
00:14:20.237 --> 00:14:23.292
and Nainoa's training in the Kahuna tradition.

353
00:14:23.714 --> 00:14:27.058
And these books contain a lot of secret knowledge,

354
00:14:27.725 --> 00:14:29.904
of the Kahuna mystics of Polynesia,

355
00:14:29.904 --> 00:14:32.246
which is not generally published.

356
00:14:33.476 --> 00:14:36.328
Now, this brings us to a very sticky point.

