00:14:36.498 --> 00:14:38.296
I was aware, in publishing these books,

358
00:14:38.296 --> 00:14:39.974
that I was trespassing.

359
00:14:40.467 --> 00:14:42.340
<v Regina>Trespassing on ancient and</v>

