00:15:48.490 --> 00:15:50.198
And they, the whole hotel, took care of our kids.

393
00:15:50.198 --> 00:15:50.798
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

394
00:15:50.798 --> 00:15:52.142
<v ->So we went up to Waimea.</v>

395
00:15:53.002 --> 00:15:56.752
And as we arrived, it started to rain torrentially.

