00:16:11.739 --> 00:16:12.917
then stopped.

404
00:16:13.207 --> 00:16:14.252
Good sign.

405
00:16:14.492 --> 00:16:15.258
<v Regina>(mumbles)</v>

406
00:16:15.258 --> 00:16:16.729
<v ->On this occasion, about 15 people</v>

