00:16:18.752 --> 00:16:21.109
And I was talking about the transformational community.

409
00:16:21.109 --> 00:16:23.469
I was talking about this very interesting slice

410
00:16:24.019 --> 00:16:25.428
of Western society,

411
00:16:25.763 --> 00:16:27.266
who are involved in the kinds of work

412
00:16:27.266 --> 00:16:29.378
that we're doing together today, alright?

413
00:16:29.378 --> 00:16:32.064
People who are interested in what we're exploring.

414
00:16:33.274 --> 00:16:35.652
Just before I began my talk, the door opened.

415
00:16:36.092 --> 00:16:38.835
And in comes this big Hawaiian man.

416
00:16:39.003 --> 00:16:40.791
Now this man's about a head taller than me.

417
00:16:40.791 --> 00:16:42.471
He's got a big ponytail down his back,

418
00:16:42.471 --> 00:16:44.767
a great big white beard down his front,

