00:16:54.447 --> 00:16:55.959
<v Regina>(laughs) You'd better be for real.</v>

424
00:16:56.509 --> 00:16:58.606
<v ->I knew that the time had come.</v>

425
00:16:58.606 --> 00:16:59.216
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

426
00:16:59.216 --> 00:17:00.812
<v ->That they had come to look me over.</v>

