455
00:17:57.735 --> 00:17:58.957
Launched into my talk.

456
00:18:00.007 --> 00:18:01.471
And about an hour and a half later,

457
00:18:01.471 --> 00:18:02.813
I came to the end,

458
00:18:02.813 --> 00:18:05.057
and I'm watching Makua all of this time.

459
00:18:05.057 --> 00:18:06.553
He's listening very seriously to what--

460
00:18:06.553 --> 00:18:07.609
everything I'm saying.

461
00:18:08.479 --> 00:18:10.189
When I came to the end of my talk,

462
00:18:11.449 --> 00:18:14.163
I had this feeling that he wanted to say something.

463
00:18:14.753 --> 00:18:16.481
It was an intuitive hit.

464
00:18:17.191 --> 00:18:19.778
And so I asked him, "Makua, I'm having this feeling

465
00:18:19.778 --> 00:18:21.502
"that there's something you would like to say."

