00:18:22.638 --> 00:18:25.762
Makua, you know, sort of looked down and smiled, and--

467
00:18:26.232 --> 00:18:28.666
Now, this was a man who traveled with 27 generations

468
00:18:28.666 --> 00:18:32.340
of his ancestral spirits in constant attendance upon him.

469
00:18:33.220 --> 00:18:35.012
He kind of leaned over this way,

470
00:18:35.012 --> 00:18:37.514
as though someone was talking in that ear.

471
00:18:37.514 --> 00:18:39.346
Then he kind of leaned over this way,

472
00:18:39.346 --> 00:18:41.092
as though someone were talking in this ear.

473
00:18:41.744 --> 00:18:43.952
And he smiled, and he stood up.

474
00:18:45.024 --> 00:18:46.806
And he looked at me, and he said,

