00:19:42.155 --> 00:19:43.699
"I wasn't pronouncing your name right.

503
00:19:44.025 --> 00:19:47.153
"They told me your name is Vessel-man."

504
00:19:47.303 --> 00:19:48.734
<v Regina>Vesselman, ah.</v>

505
00:19:48.734 --> 00:19:49.767
<v Hank>That you are the vessel--</v>
<v Regina>Yes.</v>

506
00:19:49.767 --> 00:19:50.801
<v ->Like the canoe.</v>

507
00:19:50.801 --> 00:19:53.199
And he's looking at me, to see if I'm getting it yet.

508
00:19:53.199 --> 00:19:55.091
And of course, I'm going into shock,

509
00:19:55.091 --> 00:19:57.263
