00:20:09.083 --> 00:20:10.189
<v ->Now, for starters,</v>

520
00:20:10.725 --> 00:20:13.879
Huna is not the word for the Hawaiian spiritual tradition.

521
00:20:13.879 --> 00:20:15.705
So whenever you read a book on Huna,

522
00:20:15.705 --> 00:20:17.443
it's written by an outsider,

523
00:20:17.779 --> 00:20:19.247
who doesn't know the deep knowledge.

524
00:20:20.477 --> 00:20:22.605
This man is watching me, as all these thoughts

525
00:20:22.605 --> 00:20:24.607
are going through my mind, right?

526
00:20:25.487 --> 00:20:26.676
And he says, "Don't worry.

527
00:20:26.676 --> 00:20:28.920
"We Hawaiians don't write. We talk.

528
00:20:29.240 --> 00:20:31.785
"And we share what we find in our hearts with eachother.

529
00:20:32.505 --> 00:20:36.183
"But in your tradition, it's in your culture to write.

530
00:20:36.503 --> 00:20:39.538
"And so the ancestors have asked me to say to you, today,

531
00:20:39.538 --> 00:20:41.496
"in front of all these people here,

532
00:20:41.496 --> 00:20:44.136
"that everything you wrote in your book is true.

533
00:20:44.136 --> 00:20:46.182
"And we Hawaiians support you.

534
00:20:46.182 --> 00:20:47.634
"Keep spreading the word.

535
00:20:47.634 --> 00:20:48.844
"You're making my job easy."

536
00:20:48.844 --> 00:20:49.834
(Regina laughs softly)

537
00:20:49.834 --> 00:20:52.034
Now this was the beginning of a most unusual friendship.

538
00:20:52.744 --> 00:20:55.943
Makua walked over to me, laughing-- everybody was crying,

539
00:20:55.943 --> 00:20:58.033
because this was such a moving experience.

540
00:20:58.733 --> 00:21:00.182
He walked over to me and said,

541
00:21:00.522 --> 00:21:02.625
"We should have a meeting before you leave the island."

542
00:21:04.215 --> 00:21:05.295
We had our meeting.

543
00:21:05.837 --> 00:21:08.433
He and his partner Nina, me and my wife Jill.

544
00:21:08.433 --> 00:21:11.909
We met right on the edge of the Kilauea crater.

545
00:21:12.499 --> 00:21:16.423
That big active volcano on Mauna Loa's Southeastern side.

546
00:21:16.996 --> 00:21:19.752
We spent a whole day together, getting to know eachother.

547
00:21:20.472 --> 00:21:23.493
And at the end of that day, he gave me a gift.

548
00:21:24.233 --> 00:21:27.607
He gave me a bowl, a Hawaiian wooden bowl.

549
00:21:28.655 --> 00:21:29.832
And he said to me,

550
00:21:30.252 --> 00:21:32.437
"When each one of us comes into the world,

551
00:21:33.001 --> 00:21:35.033
"we came in with a bowl of light.

552
00:21:36.015 --> 00:21:39.477
"This is the light that's the gift from our oversoul,

553
00:21:40.041 --> 00:21:41.239
"our higher self,

554
00:21:41.239 --> 00:21:43.891
"which divided itself, before we came in,

555
00:21:43.891 --> 00:21:46.011
"and sent in a seed of its light."

556
00:21:46.619 --> 00:21:49.303
He said, "That bowl of light nourishes us and sustains us

557
00:21:49.303 --> 00:21:50.807
"as we pass through life.

558
00:21:51.459 --> 00:21:53.989
"But every time we step into the negative polarity,

559
00:21:54.729 --> 00:21:57.521
"every time we injure someone with our thoughts,

560
00:21:57.521 --> 00:21:59.277
"or our words, or our deeds.

561
00:21:59.555 --> 00:22:02.070
"every time we take something that doesn't belong to us,

562
00:22:03.140 --> 00:22:04.878
"every time we achieve success at the expense of

563
00:22:04.878 --> 00:22:06.492
"somebody else's failure,

564
00:22:07.232 --> 00:22:08.926
"it's like you put a stone in your bowl,

565
00:22:08.926 --> 00:22:10.474
"and some of your light goes out."

566
00:22:11.324 --> 00:22:12.534
He said, "Life is long,

567
00:22:12.534 --> 00:22:15.394
"and surely, surely, our bowl of light

568
00:22:15.394 --> 00:22:17.184
"begins to fill up with stones,

569
00:22:17.682 --> 00:22:19.802
"until there's almost no light coming out anymore."

570
00:22:20.586 --> 00:22:21.958
He said, "You know what you do then?"

571
00:22:22.770 --> 00:22:25.244
And of course, my wife and I are hanging on every word.

572
00:22:25.244 --> 00:22:26.094
I said, "What?"

573
00:22:26.094 --> 00:22:27.076
He said, "That's easy."

574
00:22:27.076 --> 00:22:28.924
And he picked up the wooden bowl, and he turned it over,

575
00:22:28.924 --> 00:22:30.112
and he said, "You just dump them--

576
00:22:30.112 --> 00:22:31.124
<v Regina>Dumped out all the rocks. (laughs)</v>

577
00:22:31.124 --> 00:22:32.606
<v ->Dumped out all the rocks.</v>

578
00:22:32.884 --> 00:22:34.034
And he laughed.

579
00:22:34.034 --> 00:22:36.132
He said, "But when you reach that point,

580
00:22:37.482 --> 00:22:39.998
"that's when you become a spiritual warrior."

581
00:22:40.634 --> 00:22:42.892
Now, he used this word "warrior" with deliberation,

582
00:22:43.212 --> 00:22:45.142
because Makua was in the Marine Corp,

583
00:22:45.142 --> 00:22:47.782
and he was a warrior, right?

584
00:22:47.782 --> 00:22:49.674
90 tours of duty in Vietnam.

585
00:22:49.674 --> 00:22:50.268
<v Regina>Mmm.</v>

586
00:22:50.268 --> 00:22:52.138
<v ->Five wars, starting with Beirut.</v>

587
00:22:52.138 --> 00:22:52.919
<v Regina>Mmm.</v>

588
00:22:52.919 --> 00:22:54.129
<v ->He was a warrior.</v>

589
00:22:55.489 --> 00:22:58.025
He said, "When you become a spiritual warrior,

590
00:22:58.025 --> 00:22:59.255
"your path is narrow.

591
00:22:59.468 --> 00:23:03.592
"And it's constrained by three sacred directives."

592
00:23:04.462 --> 00:23:05.616
<v Hank>They call them kapus--</v>
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

593
00:23:05.616 --> 00:23:07.014
<v Hank>in Hawaiian.</v>
<v Regina>Right.</v>

594
00:23:07.014 --> 00:23:08.584
<v ->Three sacred kapus.</v>

595
00:23:08.584 --> 00:23:10.028
He said, "The first kapu.

596
00:23:11.478 --> 00:23:14.074
"Love all that you see,

597
00:23:15.254 --> 00:23:16.516
"with humility."

598
00:23:18.466 --> 00:23:20.041
Love what you see.

599
00:23:20.666 --> 00:23:22.250
Get in touch with your aloha,

600
00:23:22.250 --> 00:23:25.321
and extend that aloha to all that you see,

601
00:23:25.954 --> 00:23:27.868
cause that's where you find your humility.

602
00:23:28.191 --> 00:23:29.981
That can only be done through humility.

603
00:23:31.029 --> 00:23:32.863
He said, "I've worked on that one for seven years."

604
00:23:34.615 --> 00:23:35.789
"Number two.

605
00:23:36.485 --> 00:23:41.025
"Live all that you feel, with reverance."

606
00:23:42.315 --> 00:23:44.083
Live what you feel with reverance.

607
00:23:44.229 --> 00:23:46.407
This reverance, this act of respect,

608
00:23:46.407 --> 00:23:48.879
this is where indigenous mind begins.

609
00:23:49.267 --> 00:23:50.653
You see, Western mind,

610
00:23:51.743 --> 00:23:53.997
Western mind begins with dominion.

611
00:23:54.507 --> 00:23:55.840
Control.

612
00:23:56.690 --> 00:23:58.986
Indigenous mind begins with respect.

613
00:23:59.704 --> 00:24:00.702
With reverance.

614
00:24:02.416 --> 00:24:04.558
He said, "I've worked on that one for seven years."

615
00:24:05.342 --> 00:24:07.066
Then finally, "Number three.

616
00:24:07.696 --> 00:24:12.696
"Know all that you possess, with discipline."

617
00:24:14.516 --> 00:24:16.716
Cause this is where you find your self discipline.

618
00:24:16.716 --> 00:24:19.114
If you're gonna walk the spiritual path,

619
00:24:19.734 --> 00:24:22.152
you have to come from a place of self discipline.

620
00:24:22.152 --> 00:24:24.140
Otherwise, nothing works right.

621
00:24:25.012 --> 00:24:27.606
So, he laid these three directives on me.

622
00:24:27.986 --> 00:24:31.018
And you know, I'm thinking, "Wow, this is really something."

623
00:24:31.018 --> 00:24:32.668
This was the beginning of our friendship,

624
00:24:32.668 --> 00:24:36.100
and over an eight year period, until he passed in 2004,

625
00:24:36.100 --> 00:24:38.102
whenever my wife and I went to Hawaii,

626
00:24:38.102 --> 00:24:40.280
we would spend anywhere from a day to

627
00:24:40.280 --> 00:24:43.052
two or three, four days with him and his partner Nina.

628
00:24:43.472 --> 00:24:46.504
And during this time, he shared with me

629
00:24:46.504 --> 00:24:48.762
an enormous amount of knowledge,

630
00:24:48.762 --> 00:24:50.478
from the Kahuna tradition,

631
00:24:50.478 --> 00:24:52.402
none of which has been published, and of course,

632
00:24:53.482 --> 00:24:55.219
I don't know if any of it ever will be.

633
00:24:55.219 --> 00:24:56.947
But in the workshops and seminars,

634
00:24:57.937 --> 00:25:00.229
very often we get into discussions.

635
00:25:00.573 --> 00:25:03.113
So it becomes shared in the oral tradition.

636
00:25:03.113 --> 00:25:03.653
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

637
00:25:03.653 --> 00:25:05.197
<v ->Which is the way that it always was.</v>

638
00:25:05.197 --> 00:25:05.893
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

639
00:25:05.893 --> 00:25:07.105
<v ->You know, when we teach at Esalen,</v>

640
00:25:07.105 --> 00:25:08.139
when we teach at Omega,

641
00:25:08.139 --> 00:25:09.415
when we teach at Crossings,

642
00:25:09.415 --> 00:25:11.373
when we teach in Hawaii, you know.

643
00:25:11.373 --> 00:25:14.651
All of these seminar and workshop centers

644
00:25:14.651 --> 00:25:18.611
allow us to come and share what we have to offer.

645
00:25:20.261 --> 00:25:22.256
Now, you wanted to talk about the soul.

646
00:25:22.256 --> 00:25:24.558
<v Regina>Yes, and in the Kahuna tradition,</v>

647
00:25:24.558 --> 00:25:26.492
and in what you have learned,

648
00:25:26.492 --> 00:25:30.138
again, without revealing anything that should be--

649
00:25:30.138 --> 00:25:31.590
should not be passed on,

650
00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:37.009
the Kahuna tradition has particular understanding

651
00:25:37.009 --> 00:25:39.613
of the soul, its parts and its functions.

652
00:25:40.089 --> 00:25:43.037
And so, I wanted you to talk about that a little bit,

653
00:25:43.037 --> 00:25:43.609
if you will.

654
00:25:43.609 --> 00:25:44.973
<v ->Well, it was through my experiences,</v>

655
00:25:44.973 --> 00:25:46.535
which are recorded in the Vision--

656
00:25:46.535 --> 00:25:48.554
in the Spiritwalker trilogy,

657
00:25:49.273 --> 00:25:52.220
that I learned that the Hawaiians understand

658
00:25:52.220 --> 00:25:54.574
that we have, not one, but three souls.

659
00:25:55.724 --> 00:25:57.993
I also discovered that the Inuit

660
00:25:58.473 --> 00:25:59.951
believe we have three souls.

661
00:25:59.951 --> 00:26:00.611
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

662
00:26:00.611 --> 00:26:02.569
The Lakota, three souls.

663
00:26:02.569 --> 00:26:04.535
The Cherokee, three souls.

664
00:26:04.535 --> 00:26:07.757
The Orisha tradition of Africa, three souls.

665
00:26:07.757 --> 00:26:10.682
The Shuar of the Amazon, three souls.

666
00:26:11.471 --> 00:26:12.615
Now this is quite interesting.

667
00:26:12.615 --> 00:26:17.081
I have no idea how widely this knowledge was once held,

668
00:26:17.081 --> 00:26:19.985
in the indigenous world, because so much has been lost,

669
00:26:19.985 --> 00:26:21.819
through Christian missionary activity.

670
00:26:22.812 --> 00:26:24.550
But if I were to summarize the way in which

671
00:26:24.550 --> 00:26:27.048
the Kahunas view the three souls,

672
00:26:27.048 --> 00:26:28.598
we could begin with the higher self,

673
00:26:28.598 --> 00:26:29.838
the oversoul.

674
00:26:30.006 --> 00:26:31.862
The immortal, spiritual soul.

675
00:26:32.756 --> 00:26:35.176
Which is who we are there, right?

676
00:26:35.176 --> 00:26:38.973
That soul exists always, eternally, in the upper worlds.

677
00:26:39.500 --> 00:26:41.984
In what Judeo Christians call "Heaven".

678
00:26:41.984 --> 00:26:43.775
And Islamic people call "Paradise".

679
00:26:43.775 --> 00:26:45.689
That aspect of our self resides there.

680
00:26:45.689 --> 00:26:46.393
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

681
00:26:46.753 --> 00:26:48.498
Now before we come into life,

682
00:26:48.758 --> 00:26:50.771
the oversoul divides itself,

683
00:26:50.771 --> 00:26:53.747
and it sends down a seed of its energy.

684
00:26:53.957 --> 00:26:55.771
This is very much like a hologram,

685
00:26:55.771 --> 00:26:58.908
in the sense that that seed contains everything,

686
00:26:58.908 --> 00:27:01.262
which is recorded in the oversoul field.

687
00:27:02.742 --> 00:27:05.713
Interestingly, the vehicle of transfer

688
00:27:05.713 --> 00:27:08.573
to the new embodiment for a new life,

689
00:27:09.482 --> 00:27:10.597
is the breath.

690
00:27:11.557 --> 00:27:13.669
What the Hawaiians call the "Ha".

691
00:27:13.669 --> 00:27:14.439
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

692
00:27:14.439 --> 00:27:15.319
<v ->Ha.</v>

693
00:27:15.319 --> 00:27:17.387
Ha, as in, aloha.

694
00:27:17.777 --> 00:27:19.786
Alo means face to face.

695
00:27:19.786 --> 00:27:22.421
Ha is the divine breath of life.

696
00:27:23.240 --> 00:27:25.027
And when I say aloha to you, it means,

697
00:27:25.217 --> 00:27:27.011
"The God in me greets the Goddess in you."

698
00:27:27.491 --> 00:27:28.391
Alright?

699
00:27:28.933 --> 00:27:31.269
Now, the vehicle of transfer, the breath.

700
00:27:31.269 --> 00:27:35.497
When the embodiment is being born from its mother's womb,

701
00:27:35.497 --> 00:27:37.293
and it takes its first breath,

702
00:27:37.293 --> 00:27:38.437
(breathes in deeply)

703
00:27:38.977 --> 00:27:42.639
that seed of light descends and takes up residence.

704
00:27:43.062 --> 00:27:43.774
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

705
00:27:44.214 --> 00:27:47.840
Now, as this seed of light comes into the new being,

706
00:27:47.840 --> 00:27:48.896
for the new life,

707
00:27:48.896 --> 00:27:51.731
it encounters a distinct and separate soul,

708
00:27:51.731 --> 00:27:53.249
which is already in residence.

709
00:27:53.709 --> 00:27:56.684
This is the soul of the body, the body soul,

710
00:27:56.684 --> 00:27:59.090
what Hawaiians call "unihipili".

711
00:27:59.478 --> 00:28:01.378
There are lots of fancy words for these

712
00:28:01.378 --> 00:28:02.646
different aspects of the self.

713
00:28:02.646 --> 00:28:04.450
We'll just use the term body soul.

714
00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:07.184
Now, the body soul find its source

715
00:28:07.504 --> 00:28:10.173
from mom and dad.

716
00:28:10.781 --> 00:28:13.487
Because in the same way that there's a genetic template,

717
00:28:13.487 --> 00:28:16.061
that accompanies the sperm and the egg,

718
00:28:16.061 --> 00:28:20.008
there's also a psychic, spiritual, energetic template,

719
00:28:20.008 --> 00:28:22.529
that accompanies the sperm and the egg.

720
00:28:22.529 --> 00:28:26.775
And that spiritual complex merges at fertilization,

721
00:28:26.775 --> 00:28:28.229
to form a unity.

722
00:28:28.733 --> 00:28:31.439
And its within that body soul,

723
00:28:31.439 --> 00:28:34.497
within that energetic, spiritual component,

724
00:28:35.237 --> 00:28:38.407
that the embryo grows into a fetus which eventually

725
00:28:38.407 --> 00:28:40.057
takes form as the individual

726
00:28:40.057 --> 00:28:41.979
who's ready to be born into life.

727
00:28:42.961 --> 00:28:46.570
Now, this body soul contains all ancestral imprints,

728
00:28:46.570 --> 00:28:48.910
from both the mother's and father's lineages.

729
00:28:49.038 --> 00:28:51.168
This is why we do things which are reminiscent of

730
00:28:51.168 --> 00:28:53.268
this ancestor or that ancestor.

731
00:28:53.268 --> 00:28:54.562
<v Regina>Not just genetically,</v>

732
00:28:54.562 --> 00:28:56.784
but also socially and learned behaviors.

733
00:28:56.784 --> 00:28:57.708
<v Hank>Patterns of behavior--</v>

734
00:28:57.708 --> 00:28:58.412
<v Regina>Patterns of behavior, yes.</v>

735
00:28:58.412 --> 00:28:59.380
<v ->Patterns of expression.</v>

736
00:28:59.380 --> 00:29:00.634
Patterns of character.

737
00:29:00.634 --> 00:29:01.316
<v Regina>Right.</v>

738
00:29:01.316 --> 00:29:01.764
<v ->Right?</v>

739
00:29:01.764 --> 00:29:02.774
<v Regina>Belief systems.</v>

740
00:29:02.774 --> 00:29:03.936
<v ->That's right.</v>

741
00:29:04.226 --> 00:29:06.621
Now, the body soul has very specific functions.

742
00:29:06.767 --> 00:29:08.483
If I were to just list them on my fingers.

743
00:29:08.733 --> 00:29:11.761
Number one, this is where your memory banks are stored.

744
00:29:12.261 --> 00:29:13.721
This is where your memories are.

745
00:29:14.481 --> 00:29:17.085
Number two, it's the source of all of our

746
00:29:17.085 --> 00:29:18.625
emotions and feelings,

747
00:29:18.625 --> 00:29:21.387
which is why Deepak and others call it the emotional body.

748
00:29:21.991 --> 00:29:23.069
Number three.

749
00:29:23.489 --> 00:29:28.245
It's the aspect of ourselves, which perceives the other.

750
00:29:28.245 --> 00:29:29.409
The other world out there,

751
00:29:29.409 --> 00:29:31.759
as well as the other in there.

752
00:29:31.759 --> 00:29:33.993
It's the interface between the self and the other,

753
00:29:33.993 --> 00:29:34.957
the perceiver.

754
00:29:36.057 --> 00:29:39.441
Number four, the entire operation of the physical body,

755
00:29:39.441 --> 00:29:41.751
including its repair and restoration,

756
00:29:41.751 --> 00:29:43.335
is under its direct control.

757
00:29:43.335 --> 00:29:46.283
That means, the inner healer, is in the body soul.

758
00:29:46.283 --> 00:29:48.154
The body soul is programmed to do this.

759
00:29:48.964 --> 00:29:52.115
Number five, all of our habitual and learned behavior

760
00:29:52.115 --> 00:29:53.875
emerges from the body soul,

761
00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:55.723
because the body soul function is memory.

762
00:29:56.493 --> 00:29:59.518
Number six, it's programmed to grow,

763
00:29:59.518 --> 00:30:01.767
to increase and become more.

764
00:30:01.767 --> 00:30:04.482
It's not programmed to repress, deny and contain.

765
00:30:04.482 --> 00:30:05.230
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

766
00:30:05.230 --> 00:30:07.256
<v ->Alright? Which is why we get into so much trouble--</v>

767
00:30:07.256 --> 00:30:07.718
<v Regina>Right.</v>

768
00:30:07.718 --> 00:30:11.222
<v ->when we repress, deny, or hold negative memories,</v>

769
00:30:11.222 --> 00:30:13.514
negative emotions, negative thoughts within us.

770
00:30:13.514 --> 00:30:14.362
<v Regina>Disease is the result--</v>

771
00:30:14.362 --> 00:30:15.506
<v Hank>It disrupts--</v>
<v Regina>Yes.</v>

772
00:30:15.506 --> 00:30:16.246
<v ->the pattern.</v>

773
00:30:16.246 --> 00:30:18.010
The matrix of our energetic field,

774
00:30:18.010 --> 00:30:19.804
which is a precursor to illness.

775
