1066
00:41:41.022 --> 00:41:43.146
Theta waves are just above those,

1067
00:41:43.516 --> 00:41:47.538
at four to seven Hertz, four to seven cycles, per second,

1068
00:41:47.538 --> 00:41:50.794
where meditators go, zen masters go,

1069
00:41:50.794 --> 00:41:54.072
Yogis go there, psychic healers, trance mediums,

1070
00:41:54.072 --> 00:41:54.994
Shamans go there.

1071
00:41:54.994 --> 00:41:56.310
I mean, this has been measured.

1072
00:41:56.932 --> 00:41:59.118
Above theta waves are alpha waves,

1073
00:41:59.118 --> 00:42:01.018
which are kind of like a resting state.

1074
00:42:01.018 --> 00:42:02.264
You're awake and you're aware,

1075
00:42:02.264 --> 00:42:04.838
