1076
00:42:04.838 --> 00:42:07.165
So you're not particularly doing anything.

1077
00:42:07.165 --> 00:42:10.481
But then, they fire at roughly eight to 13 per second,

1078
00:42:10.481 --> 00:42:13.189
and above those, are the beta brainwaves states,

1079
00:42:13.189 --> 00:42:14.949
where we're focused, where we're conscious,

1080
00:42:14.949 --> 00:42:15.895
where we're doing things.

1081
00:42:15.895 --> 00:42:17.637
We're concentrating, you're working.

1082
00:42:17.637 --> 00:42:20.955
Roughly 13 to 20, 25 per second,

1083
00:42:20.955 --> 00:42:24.981
generating, roughly, eight to 10 to 15 microvolts

1084
00:42:24.981 --> 00:42:26.991
of amplitude in the brain.

