00:43:13.232 --> 00:43:14.491
That's way out there.

1102
00:43:14.491 --> 00:43:14.975
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

1103
00:43:14.975 --> 00:43:18.221
<v ->Generating between 30 and 40, 50 microvolts of amplitude.</v>

1104
00:43:18.221 --> 00:43:18.834
<v Regina>Mmhmm.</v>

1105
00:43:18.834 --> 00:43:19.907
<v ->He did it twice.</v>

